title: Netflix Stand-up Specials
description:
Netflix pushes out stand-up specials at a steady clip. We talk about two of our recent favorites, Jerry Seinfeld's '23 Hours to Kill' and Patton Oswalt's 'I Love Everything.'

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Rob Harvilla
